{"tid":1156441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[獻計] 要打贏中美貿易戰，只可以用呢招！","createTime":"2019-05-15T15:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T17:11:30.000Z","uid":29917,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"53f0b2705b01a350bde6058f6bdc4b2dc4f02e1e","tid":1156441,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T15:17:13.000Z","msg":"好多年前，有一個朋友係上海迪士尼工作，發生過一件事之後佢就翻左香港無再做。 <br />\n故事係有一家人去上海迪士尼玩，佢係場內突然向迪士尼職員發爛，要求迪士尼賠償酒店，車錢同埋入場費，再要額外既錢。 <br />\n<br />\n咁正路迪士尼職員梗係唔理你架啦，好，咁老豆就出絕招 <br />\n<br />\n佢一把把咁打自己個仔，打到個仔喊，職員唔賠，佢就繼續打，然後同職員講，你唔賠就繼續打。打到個細路鬼哭神嚎，呼天搶地，到最後職員就唯有向佢地一家人作出賠償。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n習總要打贏呢場貿易戰，好簡單，打自己國民，打到佢地流淚流血，美國佬唔取消25%關稅，就繼續打，打到歐洲各國叫美國佬停，打到英國，澳洲南美非洲各國都叫美國佬停，唔停繼續打!!!!!! <br />\n<br />\n咁呢場貿易戰就一定贏硬！"},{"pid":"7696deef3cd47a0d4583ab33628cbdd3b39de4b0","tid":1156441,"uid":176166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T15:41:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4c5313b82ca45dfab3e0096e1593b50c665e209","tid":1156441,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T16:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dccfcda24c4d79a7eca34ae45ec7f46cf172c1bc","tid":1156441,"uid":146949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T16:45:45.000Z","msg":"打埋香港效果會唔會更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9210ab57860d8a9810123cbc4934b4c704f59c","tid":1156441,"uid":87723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T16:57:43.000Z","msg":"逃學威龍見家長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a11b7b019da88750abe8a038ede9e4d7d23fee","tid":1156441,"uid":42751,"like":0,"di